title: Rogue One: A Star Wars Story
description: You know about the Death Star; right? No? What are you even doing here? I don't mean to gatekeep; but why do you even have this app if you don't know what the Death Star is? Go watch Episode IV; and come back if you liked it... Did you watch it? That was pretty cool; huh? Anyways; they explain how they got the plans for the Death Star in this one. That may not have been a burning question you had; but here's your answer.
